          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "：深只读视图，防止子组件改父状态；"
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "shallowReactive"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 只代理第一层。和性能优化题一起说「先 profiling 再 shallow」更稳。"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "q-computed",
      "navLabel": "computed 与 method",
      "question": "computed 和 methods 里写个函数有啥区别？",
      "answer": [
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "computed(() => ...)"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
