    {
      "id": "q-nexttick",
      "navLabel": "nextTick",
      "question": "Vue 的 nextTick 是干啥的？",
      "answer": [
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "当你在一次同步代码里改了响应式数据，DOM 更新是"
          },
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "异步批量刷新的"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "——立刻读 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "el.textContent"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 可能还是旧值。"
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "nextTick(() => { ... })"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 把回调排到本次 DOM 更新队列之后，保证能拿到更新后的 DOM，常用于焦点、量尺寸、接第三方非 Vue 库。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "底层用微任务（Promise）或 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "MutationObserver"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 等把刷新推迟到当前调用栈结束；和 React 的 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "flushSync"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 对比能说清「默认批量、必要时再同步」即可。"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
